Package: bblocks
Type: Package
Title: Builds Blocks for Better Randomization
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Sara", "Gong", email = "saragong@usc.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: bblocks is designed to prepare data for blocked, or stratified, randomization. Given a minimum block size and a set of covariates, bblocks efficiently partitions the covariate space into subgroups with reduced heterogeneity.
